Requeriments:

	* libSDL (*1)
	* libSDL_image (*1)
	* libSDL_mixer (*1)

	(*1) = see the official web site of SDL www.libsdl.org


Steps for root:

	./configure
	make
	su
	make install
	exit
	chanta


Steps for other user (<user>):

	./configure --prefix=/home/<user>/test/chanta
	make
	make install
	cd /home/<user>/test/chanta/bin
	./chanta
